description:
Go Go Neptune Ranger! Grab the Hero Sentai Brave Ranger [Brave Purple] outfit today! Neptune can also wear the suit with our without the helmet! Players can even mix-n-match with the *animal sets for fun!

*Animal Set(s) are not included in the Hero Sentai Brave Ranger outfits.

Note: Players can access the Hero Sentai Brave Ranger [Brave Purple] outfit by going to the Menu and scrolling to the Equipment section.
name: Hero Sentai Brave Ranger [Brave Purple]
